{"tid":683743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司徒華：即使六四發生，我仍堅決支持「回歸」","createTime":"2018-05-30T02:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T15:48:07.000Z","uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"a12287f90c044bcca261840fda082248885e0df3","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"司徒華：即使六四發生，我仍堅決支持「回歸」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=74fe1800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=33edeefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e2a37cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者：「你指出中國過去幾十年出現很多問題，但在中英會談時，你很早便支持中國收回香港的主權，為什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n司徒華：「香港本來就是中國的地方，回歸母體是必然的事實。雖然當時的政權很多地方我並不同意，但假如一個國家對屬於自己的土地也不收回，沒有民族自尊，這個國家和政權是要不得的。我們作為中國人，回歸祖國與十一億人民同命運是很應該的。過去百多年來，我們好像很『僥倖』與中華民族的苦難脫離，但亦有點自咎。所以不論前景如何，我還是支持收回主權，『六‧四』事件並沒有改變我的看法。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; &mdash; 1989年9月1日香港電台節目「新聞天地」專訪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 馮玉蓮《走向九七：政壇精英訪談錄》（1990）<br />\n司徒華回歸香港九七六四<br />\nOne clap, two clap, three clap, forty?<br />\nBy clapping more or less, you can signal to us which stories really stand out.<br />\n<br />\nGo to the profile of Julian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nJulian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/h0julian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fh0julian&d=5kzrlEfzlIokQJ1uteSlY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=bb96b835\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/h0julian</a>"},{"pid":"b04018f1bbcdf7573d85403c1df3b48f0342a6e8","tid":683743,"uid":59030,"like":136,"dislike":2,"score":134,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:57:58.000Z","msg":"食屎狗<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n司徒廢老兩腳一伸個結果要我地受<br />\n正仆街"},{"pid":"4a97163f72c438af9dbd08dd016a5e69f9ce643b","tid":683743,"uid":85659,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"當年個位歲數我已經同屋企人講<br />\n呢條友害撚死人家<br />\n無人信我 仲同我講愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459e0dc42dc9ec5f244e80202fd498a3dd0ba631","tid":683743,"uid":66798,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"司徒華落地獄"},{"pid":"0fbce435fe41d0c856c66196d4dd0d5381f7386e","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14f3fc6759ec9fddbffaaa79893e8a6edccb628","tid":683743,"uid":51701,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"共諜"},{"pid":"5e22ad76f54b1dc69bd5c142996efb862219b2a2","tid":683743,"uid":103207,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"司屠老狗真係冇屌錯"},{"pid":"40a5bc616f1b45b83f4ed56e52118f920a93ee38","tid":683743,"uid":18251,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"佢啲屋企人又有無回歸祖國定移燃曬民呀？<br />\n死仆街司徒老狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68e4368097a70f69e75eb556709bec7a2654b9f","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor