"2018-06-03T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本佢就係共諜"},{"pid":"5c81aaf0710e41cdfa773b60bf84a6a280076f6b","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d535cc59f436b34cb72b62a43ac248255ee00ca","tid":683743,"uid":38426,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"呢啲民主老人真係食古不化<br />\n宜家兩腳一伸 全香港7百萬人陪你受罪<br />\n屌你老母司徒華下世返支那做豬啦"},{"pid":"1116ef7f5c244e845199bc388bea2295eead59ab","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4711212082f26a3f08f1540e9eace4e04a9a9887","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6dc27d302b7c38a6f087ef288ffeb446861125","tid":683743,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"依家D老坑死之前點都要放啲老鼠屎落煲粥度等下幾代去食，回歸係咁，領匯係咁，依家搵地起樓又係咁"},{"pid":"d3d357d1e5d8fd8d81e168b4a6ba7e4f00ef7351","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b223048d0180931f59b61e4b429cb4b6d13d5f7","tid":683743,"uid":143372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12287f90c044bcca261840fda082248885e0df3","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"司徒華：即使六四發生，我仍堅決支持「回歸」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110221_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=74fe1800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110231_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=33edeefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F110236_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e2a37cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者：「你指出中國過去幾十年出現很多問題，但在中英會談時，你很早便支持中國收回香港的主權，為什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n司徒華：「香港本來就是中國的地方，回歸母體是必然的事實。雖然當時的政權很多地方我並不同意，但假如一個國家對屬於自己的土地也不收回，沒有民族自尊，這個國家和政權是要不得的。我們作為中國人，回歸祖國與十一億人民同命運是很應該的。過去百多年來，我們好像很『僥倖』與中華民族的苦難脫離，但亦有點自咎。所以不論前景如何，我還是支持收回主權，『六‧四』事件並沒有改變我的看法。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; &mdash; 1989年9月1日香港電台節目「新聞天地」專訪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 馮玉蓮《走向九七：政壇精英訪談錄》（1990）<br />\n司徒華回歸香港九七六四<br />\nOne clap, two clap, three clap, forty?<br />\nBy clapping more or less, you can signal to us which stories really stand out.<br />\n<br />\nGo to the profile of Julian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nJulian Ho 何曦偉<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/h0julian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fh0julian&d=5kzrlEfzlIokQJ1uteSlY5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=bb96b835\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/h0julian</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0d2cf31b9b7a99b1265ddd5c4929d7cd96c9cd27","tid":683743,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"佢好彩死得早<br />\n唔係今日個朵一定臭到仆街"},{"pid":"f60c3598223d671fd27b0aa6b2e3d5e9b75f50e8","tid":683743,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" c